Document: VisualShaderNodeVectorDecompose
Path: godot/classes/class_visualshadernodevectordecompose.rst
Summary: This class takes a vec2, vec3, or vec4 input and decomposes it into individual scalar components, allowing each component to be used as a separate output in shader graphs.